                    "type": "CallExpression",
                    "name": "setDesc",
                    "source": "Requires restart of Obsidian. If enabled, when the cursor is in a table, enter advances to the next row. Disabling this can help avoid conflicting with tag or CJK autocompletion. If disabling, bind \"Go to ...\" in the Obsidian Hotkeys settings.",
                    "target": "需要重启 Obsidian。启用后，当光标位于表格中时，回车键将跳至下一行。禁用此功能可避免与标签或中日韩文自动补全冲突。如果禁用，请在 Obsidian 热键设置中绑定“转到...”。"
